  <span id="freeText2357050565188844882" style="display:none">This book started really well but then turned to a bore for me. The score on Audible and GoodReads is really high, suprisingly!I think the writer wanted to create a twist, shocking ending, however when you think about the whole thing, the story is just too illogical. Thinking about science and biological possibilities...<br /><br />The plot was dragging after the second half of the book, I really got bored at one point. As a usual suspense reader it is easy to put two and two together and the story is very predictable. <br /><br /> Too difficult to tell without giving out spoilers- overall, can't say I liked it..</span>
